C Compliance & Rejections FAQs Answered to Get You Approved","previewImage":{"childrenImageSharp":[{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/378dbbc8777b5dfef5021a1cd56a6f65/f3ceb/blog-banner-image-3-.webp","srcSet":"/static/378dbbc8777b5dfef5021a1cd56a6f65/f3ceb/blog-banner-image-3-.webp 1000w","sizes":"1000px"},"sources":[]},"width":1000,"height":389}}]}},"id":"fdca717f-bec8-57df-a865-cf0dccfe640f","fields":{"slug":"10dlc-compliance-faqs-answered/"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"articleType":"BLOG POST","date":"October 12, 2023","title":"Avoiding Campaign Rejections: New 10DLC Compliance Requirements to be Aware Of ","previewImage":{"childrenImageSharp":[{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/3308e368680c2a14666b7fc89b51f704/7a1b6/shutterstock_307219181.webp","srcSet":"/static/3308e368680c2a14666b7fc89b51f704/7a1b6/shutterstock_307219181.webp 1000w","sizes":"1000px"},"sources":[]},"width":1000,"height":667}}]}},"id":"87696f10-2696-53ad-9225-cc24edb69b1b","fields":{"slug":"new-campaign-guidelines/"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"articleType":"BLOG POST","date":"September 29, 2023","title":"How 10DLC Industry Changes Affect Your Customer's Experience & Retention","previewImage":{"childrenImageSharp":[{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","backgroundColor":"#485868","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/c63767a35751f8ff3af82df03c465f16/8d92a/how-10dlc-industry-changes-affect-your-customers-experience-retention.webp","srcSet":"/static/c63767a35751f8ff3af82df03c465f16/8d92a/how-10dlc-industry-changes-affect-your-customers-experience-retention.webp 1000w","sizes":"1000px"},"sources":[]},"width":1000,"height":498}}]}},"id":"85943de5-248c-50cf-9b13-ad8d3e6cb79f","fields":{"slug":"10dlc-customer-experience/"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"articleType":"BLOG POST","date":"September 01, 2023","title":"10DLC Cut Off – What Now? Mitigating Damage from the Twilio Regi